<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:32.365 --> 00:34.701
[slot machine ringing]

00:34.701 --> 00:41.708
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:46.713 --> 00:48.506
Quit while we're ahead, honey.

00:48.506 --> 00:51.051
Uh-uh.
This is your lucky day.

00:51.051 --> 00:52.594
- [coins rattling]
- all right.

00:52.594 --> 00:59.851
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:00.894 --> 01:04.064
Ladies and gentlemen,
you're gonna want to trust me,

01:04.064 --> 01:06.149
but I beg you, do not.

01:07.275 --> 01:10.111
You must be critical, doubtful.

01:10.111 --> 01:13.323
Scrutinize my every move.

01:13.323 --> 01:15.867
And if you need advice
on how to do that,

01:15.867 --> 01:17.494
just ask my wife, Celeste!

01:17.494 --> 01:19.371
