[applause]

01:19.371 --> 01:22.999
Because a magic trick
is just like a marriage.

01:23.541 --> 01:25.919
You know I'm gonna
betray you...

01:25.919 --> 01:27.545
[exhales sharply]
[laughter]

01:27.545 --> 01:30.799
But you stick around
to see exactly...

01:30.799 --> 01:32.967
how I'm going to do it.

01:32.967 --> 01:34.427
[laughter]

01:34.427 --> 01:37.555
audience: Oh!
[applause]

01:41.518 --> 01:44.646
[cheers and applause]

01:47.857 --> 01:49.818
Now it's that time of night.

01:49.818 --> 01:52.904
I need a brave soul
from the audience.

01:52.904 --> 01:54.114
Let's see what we have here.

01:54.114 --> 01:55.198
Yo, over here!

01:55.198 --> 01:56.449
Too drunk.
[laughter]

01:56.449 --> 01:58.952
Too eager.
Too handsome.

01:58.952 --> 02:00.120
Let's see.

02:00.120 --> 02:01.454
Oh, I'm sorry, young lady.

02:01.454 --> 02:03.832
