to ride the ride.

02:03.832 --> 02:06.459
[audience groans, boos]

02:06.459 --> 02:10.130
Okay, okay, I'll make
an exception just this once.

02:10.130 --> 02:13.633
[applause]

02:13.633 --> 02:16.261
