name is--

02:16.261 --> 02:17.470
psst, name?

02:17.470 --> 02:19.139
- Lizzie.
- Lizzie.

02:19.139 --> 02:20.557
Here's what we're gonna do.

02:20.557 --> 02:23.977
Before the show, I selected
three separate volunteers

02:23.977 --> 02:27.522
to draw a single card
without showing it to anyone.

02:27.522 --> 02:29.441
Can you folks
please stand up now,

02:29.441 --> 02:30.859
if you don't mind?

02:30.859 --> 02:32.110
[applause]

02:32.110 --> 02:33.153
Thank you.

02:33.153 --> 02:34.404
And, Lizzie,
can you please

02:34.404 --> 02:36.573
stand on your seat
nice and tall?

02:37.198 --> 02:38.783
Here's what we're gonna do.

02:38.783 --> 02:41.661
I'm gonna throw
this deck of cards at you.

02:41.661 --> 02:43.663
You're gonna reach up
and catch one.

02:43.663 --> 02:45.290
When you catch it,
if you catch it,

02:45.290 --> 02:47.292
take a look

02:47.292 --> 02:49.336
and say what it is, okay?

02:50.170 --> 02:51.171
Ready?

02:51.171 --> 02:52.797
On three.

02:52.797 --> 02:55.800
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

02:55.800 --> 02:56.760
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:56.760 --> 02:57.802
One.

02:57.802 --> 02:59.846
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:59.846 --> 03:00.847
