03:01.848 --> 03:02.891
Three.

03:02.891 --> 03:04.017
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:04.017 --> 03:05.602
And, Lizzie, what is the card?

03:05.602 --> 03:07.937
- The queen of hearts!
- The queen of hearts!

03:07.937 --> 03:09.856
And everyone else,
what are your cards?

03:09.856 --> 03:11.441
- Shout it out!
- The queen of hearts!

03:11.441 --> 03:13.026
