all your own ♪</i>

04:29.894 --> 04:32.188
<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:32.188 --> 04:37.610
<i>♪ Just close your eyes,
he'll be there ♪</i>

04:37.610 --> 04:39.946
You were great tonight, bug.

04:39.946 --> 04:42.323
Thanks, Dad.
You both did great too.

04:42.323 --> 04:43.783
You hear that, sweetheart?

04:43.783 --> 04:45.952
