04:53.877 --> 04:56.296
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

04:56.296 --> 04:58.840
Well,
I'm not withholding tacos.

04:58.840 --> 05:00.383
[chuckles]
Who's hungry?

05:00.383 --> 05:05.597
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:05.597 --> 05:07.974
Do not even think
of going behind that door.

05:07.974 --> 05:09.976
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:09.976 --> 05:11.061
Come on, Celeste.

05:11.061 --> 05:13.188
Just tell me
what you're working on.

05:13.188 --> 05:14.522
We're partners.

05:14.522 --> 05:15.774
If we were partners,
you would acknowledge

05:15.774 --> 05:18.443
who designed
what you are performing.

05:18.443 --> 05:22.572
Everyone knows
you're the engineer, honey.

05:22.572 --> 05:26.159
I'm just the idiot onstage
telling sexist jokes.

05:26.159 --> 05:28.286
Come on, please?

05:28.286 --> 05:29.829
Just let me take a look.
I promise I'll--

05:29.829 --> 05:33.541
I am in process,
in process on something new.

05:34.542 --> 05:37.629
