05:59.150 --> 06:02.529
Ladies and gentlemen,
you're gonna want to trust me,

06:02.529 --> 06:04.155
<i>but I beg you, do not.</i>

06:04.155 --> 06:06.533
<i>You know I'm going
to betray you,</i>

06:06.533 --> 06:08.618
<i>but you stick around to see</i>

06:08.618 --> 06:11.079
<i>exactly how I'm going
to do it.</i>

06:11.079 --> 06:12.372
<i>Trust me, do not.</i>

06:12.372 --> 06:14.040
And, Lizzie, what is the card?

06:14.040 --> 06:16.084
- <i>[distorted] Trust me.</i>
- The queen of hearts!

06:16.084 --> 06:17.502
The queen of hearts!

06:17.502 --> 06:19.004
The queen
of hearts!

06:19.004 --> 06:20.922
Night, sweetie pie.

