06:27.637 --> 06:29.806
<i>♪ It caught on in a flash ♪</i>

06:29.806 --> 06:31.433
<i>♪ They did the Mash ♪</i>

06:31.433 --> 06:33.518
Who's ready for Halloween?

06:33.518 --> 06:35.812
