10:39.431 --> 10:40.682
[chuckles]

10:41.641 --> 10:43.351
Does that hurt?

10:44.352 --> 10:45.729
Not really.

10:47.689 --> 10:49.899
I think I'm just in shock.

10:49.899 --> 10:53.361
Yeah, me too.

10:54.779 --> 10:55.822
What's your name?

10:55.822 --> 10:58.491
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:58.491 --> 11:00.410
Lizzie.

11:00.410 --> 11:01.703
What's yours?

11:02.495 --> 11:04.330
Wiley.

11:04.330 --> 11:06.624
Well, I like your costume, Wiley.

11:06.624 --> 11:08.960
It's actually
not a costume.

11:08.960 --> 11:11.463
[chuckles]
That's so cool.

11:11.463 --> 11:13.965
I've always wanted
to meet a real cowboy.

11:13.965 --> 11:16.301
That's so weird.

11:16.301 --> 11:18.970
I've always wanted
to meet a real wizard.

11:19.679 --> 11:22.307
Then I guess
it's your lucky day.

11:22.307 --> 11:29.272
<i>♪ ♪</i>

11:31.733 --> 11:32.942
<i>Sister Simone,</i>

11:32.942 --> 11:36.863
<i>you must locate
the Holy Grail.</i>

11:36.863 --> 11:39.282
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

11:39.282 --> 11:40.658
