[chuckles]

13:34.981 --> 13:37.525
<i>[mysterious music]</i>

13:37.525 --> 13:39.652
No.
Come on.

13:39.652 --> 13:43.156
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:43.156 --> 13:46.034
