to "rescue me"

13:54.959 --> 13:56.920
when I escaped.

13:56.920 --> 13:58.296
Hey, well, I must say,
for a nun,

13:58.296 --> 14:00.965
you lead quite
the exciting life.

14:00.965 --> 14:03.968
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

14:03.968 --> 14:05.679
